---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import SocialIcons from './SocialIcons.astro'


const {fullName, shortName, slogan, title, institute, profilePicture} = Astro.props
---
<div class='flex-1'>
  <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-4'>
    Welcome! I'm <span class='text-secondary'>{shortName}</span>
  </h1>
  <p class='text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4'> {slogan}</p>
  <p class='text-lg mb-6'>
    Gene Wernick is a Rabbi with a passion for education, scholarship and community. Having published his first book almost a decade ago he is set to
    release his newest work in 2026. A commentary on the importance of Tribes and the role Rabbi Ascher ben Yechiel had
    In effecting the extended family, and the ancestral ties of the Jewish People.  
    Although there are rituals and ceremonies even someone who is however alienated is still recognized as belonging.
    The book explores Jews identifying each other and antisemites identifying Jews as Jews. 
    Rabbi Wernick is available for guest lectures, pastorial care and life-cycle events in New York City or online.
  </p>
  <div class='flex gap-4'>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
</div>
<div class='size-72 lg:block hidden'>
  <!-- Add your profile image -->
  <Image
    src={profilePicture}
    alt={fullName}
    class='w-full h-full mask mask-circle size-44'
  />
</div>
